data.title: Oleoleh
data.description: Oleoleh is an application developed to make it easy for users to buy souvenirs from anywhere. This application will assist users in purchasing, looking for the nearest store and delivering souvenirs to your place with a flat delivery method and costs up to 25km.

Narma Shop itself wants to realize the convenience of shopping so as to create a mini e-commerce application, in this application the user is given the ease of buying and using delivery services in buying goods

data.title: Watong
data.description: Watong is an application to simplify franchise services with the Watong brand, which sells a variety of foods and beverages. Watong makes it easy for buyers to make purchases and take order at the time specified by the buyer.

data.title: Football Kick
data.description: FootBall Kick application is an application intended to view football match schedules,match results, match details, team details and descriptions of players in the team, this application also features favorite features to save results and can be used to install alarms for upcoming matches.
